response.original_title: Sana May Bulsa Ang Mga Spacesuits
response.overview: Instead of preparing the documents for his graduation, Prince, a graduating student, ends up grabbing the opportunity to go to the moon; conflicted to leave everything, he needs to find a way to keep the memories of his loved ones alive.
response.tagline: Grabbing the opportunity to go to the moon, he needs to find a way to keep the memories of his loved ones alive.
